org.epics.pvaccess.impl.remote.request

Interface ResponseRequest

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataResponse, SubscriptionRequest
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseRequestImpl, ChannelArrayRequestImpl, ChannelGetFieldRequestImpl, ChannelGetRequestImpl, ChannelMonitorImpl, ChannelProcessRequestImpl, ChannelPutGetRequestImpl, ChannelPutRequestImpl, ChannelRPCRequestImpl

    public interface ResponseRequest
    A request that expects an response. Responses identified by its I/O ID. This interface needs to be extended (to provide method called on response).
